reviews.review_text: At Last One of the best second sets from '92.  The band was firing away, and grooving.  Jerry was on, the band was inspiring, and even Vince sounds great.  I'm happy this show has finally arrived at archive.  One of the best of '92, and you can enjoy it at last.
